{"type":null,"faqId":45350,"title":"将荣耀盒子M321连接至电脑显示器，显示器没图像怎么办？","answer":"<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\r\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\r\n.s1{font-family:Times New Roman;}\r\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\r\n</style>\n<div>\n<p><span>\"1. 可能显示器的自动分辨率自动适配时出现问题，请调整显示器的分辨率，设置为为 1024*768。<br>\n2. 如果您用的是 HDMI 转 VGA 线连接显示器，可能是转接线有问题，建议更换转接线重试。<br>\n3. 可能是当前盒子的输出分辨率太高。请把分辨率调节至 720P，操作如下：<br>\n− 建议使用 HDMI 连接高清电视机，再进入“设置 &gt; 显示 &gt;&nbsp; HDMI 分辨率”将分辨率设置为 720P 。再将盒子重新用转接线连接显示器。<br>\n− 您也可以长按遥控器主页键&nbsp; 10s 以上。分辨率将自动修改为720P。<br>\n\" <br>\n</span></p>\n</div>","faqTypeId":247,"faqType":"显示","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"871","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556875000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":21,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"电脑显示器,没图像,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}